# [MOPS](../wg/mops.html)

## Summary

The Media Operations (MOPS) Working Group met at IETF 126. The session featured an interactive industry panel discussing local geography and operational experiences with video streaming, an update on the active working group draft `draft-ietf-mops-network-overlay-impacts`, an industry update on the Streaming Video Technology Alliance (SVTA), and a discussion regarding a proposed charter update to transition the working group from experimental to permanent status.

